WindWatcher App Privacy Policy
At bog bridges, ensuring the privacy of our users is of utmost importance. We will never share or sell your data, and we will not allow ads to be displayed in our apps.
​
The Privacy Policy for the WindWatcher Apple Watch and Apple iPhone app is simple.
​
The app does not knowingly collect any Personal Identifiable Information (PII) from users of the app, and does not knowingly share any data with advertisers or any other third parties.
​
WindWatcher does not access the Internet. The app uses Apple's iCloud services to securely update anonymous app diagnostic data to help improve the app.
​
If you have additional questions or require more information about this Privacy Policy, please contact us through email at
info@bogbridges.com
​
Consent
​
By using the WindWatcher
app, you hereby consent to this Privacy Policy and agree to its Terms and Conditions.